snippet.title: Shaakuntalam Official Trailer - Telugu | Samantha, Dev Mohan | Gunasekhar | Feb 17, 2023 Release
snippet.description:
Shaakuntalam Official Trailer - Telugu | Samantha, Dev Mohan | Gunasekhar | Feb 17, 2023 Release

Shaakuntalam Movie also in 3D, Written & Directed by Gunasekhar, Presented by Dil Raju under Sri Venkateswara Creations in collaboration with Gunaa Teamworks, Produced by Neelima Guna.

The massively mounted film Shaakuntalam based on internationally acclaimed Kalidasa‚Äôs Sanskrit play ‚ÄòAbhijnana Shakuntalam‚Äô is all set to release in Hindi, Telugu, Tamil, Malayalam & Kannada.  The story of Shaakuntalam revolves around the epic love story of Shakuntala and King Dushyant from Mahabharata, portrayed by Samantha and Dev Mohan.

The film is helmed by supremely proficient, Director Gunasekhar and marks a whimsical tale of love set in the Kashyapa Kanumalu (Kashmir), the grandeur and splendour of Dushyant‚Äôs Puru Dynasty making the film extremely exceptional.

Cast and Crew Details: 

Shaakuntalam starring Samantha, Dev Mohan, Allu Arha, Sachin Khedekar, Kabir Bedi, Dr.M Mohan Babu, Prakash Raj, Madhubala, Gautami, Aditi Balan, Ananya Nagalla, Jisshu Sengupta and others

snippet.description:
Synopsis: When Intelligence Meets Comedy
 --------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
The host, Kapil Sharma makes a rocking entry to the stage and welcomes everyone to the show. He then performs a stand-up act and entertains the audience thoroughly. He then proceeds to welcome the special guests for the night. They are none other than the great motivational speakers of our country, Gaur Gopal Das, Vivek Bindra, and Khan Sir. Their unique wit and humor end up being the highlight of the night. Watch the full episode to know more.

snippet.description:
Poem/ Letter to Birthday Boy from Amma & Achan (Written by Jan)
 
" 
Happy Birthday Ave 
We enjoyed your innocent childhood and not so explosive teens 
Excuse our inexperience , we learned the art of parenting with you.

For us , letting go may not come easy
For you , leaving behind may not come easy 
We may have to settle for a mid point 
Which allows you to explore the world and find yourself
Where the relevance of home and cuddling may slowly erode 
We may not be the cool family around and we may evolve in ways you may not approve
You may change into a person we hardly recognize 
However , trust in a lasting bond will never fade
And at some point we will exchange roles 
And you will take over the reins of life 
And today is the first step towards that 
Celebrate the light within you 
Create meaningful connections
Try out different experiences - what may fascinate you today , may lose its luster
What you don‚Äôt care for today , may become a dear thing 
You may need to travel half way around the world to find the treasure in your backyard
If you learn , in whatsoever state you are , therewith to be content, in abundance and need 
You will have a happy life 
Happy Birthday Sweetheart ‚ù§Ô∏è‚ù§Ô∏è‚ù§Ô∏è‚ù§Ô∏è

Love 
Achan , Amma & Aathu "
-----------------------------------------------------------------

snippet.title: Kya Karoon - Sanam Puri | Jaani | Jasmin Bhasin | Arvindr Khaira | Desi Melodies
snippet.description:
Desi Melodies is kicking off the year with Sanam Puri‚Äôs golden voice combined with Jaani‚Äôs lily-white lyrics and composition in the form of ‚ÄòKya Karoon‚Äô - guaranteed to give you sonic goosebumps.

‚ÄòKya Karoon‚Äô is a heart-wrenching ballad that tells the story of two lovers held together by emotive lyrics and soulful melodies, combined with Puri's smooth that transport the listener to a world of love, longing, and heartache. The music video directed by Arvindr Khaira, is a visual feast, featuring Sanam and Jasmin Bhasin in a raw yet dreamy atmosphere. As the song builds to its emotional climax, it's clear that this is a love that will stand the test of time, unwavering and true.

About Film Companion South:
Film Companion South is a division of Film Companion, founded by film critic and author Anupama Chopra. Apart from film reviews and articles, Film Companion South, with programs in Tamil, Malayalam, Telugu, and Kannada, specializes in conducting in-depth interviews with film personalities which include the likes of Kamal Hassan, Mani Ratnam, Academy Award-winner AR Rahman, Vetrimaaran, Dhanush, Yash, Sruthi Hariharan, Mahesh Babu, NTR Jr, Samantha, Aishwarya Rajesh, Ramya Krishnan, Prithviraj, Anjali Menon, Mysskin, Gautam Vasudev Menon, Rajamouli, Ram Charan, Yash, Prashanth Neel, Venkat Prabhu, Nelson, Sivakarthikeyan, Rakshit Shetty and many more. The channel has also hosted shows which open up the lesser-known facets of filmmaking with conversations with PC Sreeram, Ravi Varman, Rajiv Menon, Thota Tharani, and Academy Award-winner Resul Pookutty. In other words, Film Companion South is for those who love their cinema and are unapologetic about it.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Farq Episode 21 - [Eng Sub] - Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 9th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Written By: Imran Nazir
Directed By: Aehsun Talish
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3663 - 9 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3663: Badey Order Ki Tension
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha calls Nattu Kaka to get an update on Bagha's condition. Nattu Kaka informs him that Bagha has tried to run away multiple times and somehow he has managed to fall asleep. Nattu Kaka has locked the house so that Bagha does not escape. After his call, Jetha calls Taarak to get a piece of advice on the situation but he is stuck at work. Taarak avoids Jetha's call as the peon is keeping an eye on him. Later at night, Bapuji sees that Jetha is tensed and he decides to ask him about the matter to which Jetha explains everything to him. 

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3663, 9 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Rs 9.99 Lacs Mahindra Thar RWD | Branded Content | ICN Studio
snippet.description: We finally got the opportunity to drive the new 2023 Mahindra Thar RWD (4x2) in an around Jaipur to see if it's better as a city car. The rear wheel drive thar comes in two engine options - a 1.5-litre D117 diesel and a 2.0L petrol. We drove the 1.5-litre diesel version that is available with a 6-speed manual transmission. It's the same engine that powers the Marazzo and XUV300. It churns out 117bhp and 300Nm, which is more than enough for this version since it has shed significant weight.

snippet.description:
In the year 1999, Indian Airlines Flight IC-814 was traveling from Kathmandu to Delhi. It was carrying 180 passengers who went on to live the worst nightmare of their lives. This is their story. See how the events unfolded and how the former Indian govt under Atal Bihari Vajpayee managed the situation.

snippet.description:
#tilgudladoorecipe Til ke laddu or sesame ladoos are traditional Indian sweet balls made with sesame seeds, jaggery and cardamom powder. Til ke Laddu Recipe is a nutty, tasty, ladoo made with sesame seeds, jaggery, peanuts. Sesame laddu is a good warming winter sweet snack. Til ke laddu are high in magnesium which means they are good for the heart by lowering the blood pressure. Tilkut Recipe Til Gur Ladoo Recipe Dishes prepared from Til(sesame seeds) provide heat and energy to the body which are both necessary to beat the cold. Til Ladoo is delightfully nutty, naturally sweetened with jaggery, and protein-packed. This recipe makes the Til Gud Ke Laddu in a food processor or blender without making the jaggery syrup.

en-IN.description:
#tilgudladoorecipe Til ke laddu or sesame ladoos are traditional Indian sweet balls made with sesame seeds, jaggery and cardamom powder. Til ke Laddu Recipe is a nutty, tasty, ladoo made with sesame seeds, jaggery, peanuts. Sesame laddu is a good warming winter sweet snack. Til ke laddu are high in magnesium which means they are good for the heart by lowering the blood pressure. Tilkut Recipe Til Gur Ladoo Recipe Dishes prepared from Til(sesame seeds) provide heat and energy to the body which are both necessary to beat the cold. Til Ladoo is delightfully nutty, naturally sweetened with jaggery, and protein-packed. This recipe makes the Til Gud Ke Laddu in a food processor or blender without making the jaggery syrup.

snippet.title: CID-Mumbai Cases| CID | Officer Shreya Gets Set For A Battle With 'The Eye' |9 Jan 2023|Full Episode
snippet.description:
Daya and ACP Pradyuman get information from IB about a web hacker who along with 'The Eye.' It wants to bomb blasts and spread violence in the country. According to IB, a boy named Ajinkya is behind this. He is coming to Mumbai on the next flight, and after that, he is going to carry out bomb blasts in many parts of the country. Officer Shreya has a huge contribution to preventing these accidents. How will she solve this case? What will happen next? How will the CID team handle this case? Watch the entire episode to know more.

About CID:
-----------------
Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Farq Episode 22 Teaser - 9th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Written By: Imran Nazir
Directed By: Aehsun Talish
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Tere Bin Episode 04 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 5th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: Hostel Hudugaru Protest Song | Hostel Hudugaru Bekagiddare | Ajaneesh Loknath |Nithin Krishnamurthy
snippet.description:
Hostel Hudugaru Protest Song !!!  Kantara music director B. Ajaneesh Loknath comes with another magical creation in Nithin Krishnamurthy's directorial debut, Hostel Hudugaru Bekagiddare. The first single "Hostel Hudugaru Protest Song" sung by the Music director himself and penned by Yogarajbhat Fans is another attraction for the film. Hostel Hudugaru Bekagiddare is a one-of-a-kind found-footage comedy-drama that is set entirely inside a boy's hostel, featuring 500 new talents and a cameo by superstars, Rishab Shetty, Ramya, Pavan Kumar & Shine Shetty.  The film is made under the Gulmohar films banner in association with Varrun Studios. The director has also served as one of the four producers of the film along with Prajwal B.P., Varun Kumar, and Arvind S. Kashyap, who is handling cinematography as well and Presented by Paramvah Pictures.

Listen to the song on all your favorite Music platforms: https://bfan.link/hostel-hudugaru-protest-song

https://bit.ly/SubscribeToA2Music for more!

localized.description:
Hostel Hudugaru Protest Song !!!  Kantara music director B. Ajaneesh Loknath comes with another magical creation in Nithin Krishnamurthy's directorial debut, Hostel Hudugaru Bekagiddare. The first single "Hostel Hudugaru Protest Song" sung by the Music director himself and penned by Yogarajbhat Fans is another attraction for the film. Hostel Hudugaru Bekagiddare is a one-of-a-kind found-footage comedy-drama that is set entirely inside a boy's hostel, featuring 500 new talents and a cameo by superstars, Rishab Shetty, Ramya, Pavan Kumar & Shine Shetty.  The film is made under the Gulmohar films banner in association with Varrun Studios. The director has also served as one of the four producers of the film along with Prajwal B.P., Varun Kumar, and Arvind S. Kashyap, who is handling cinematography as well and Presented by Paramvah Pictures.

About CID:
-----------------
Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

‚ñ∫*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye‚Ä¶ parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!


Jaanne ke liye dekhiye #RadhaKrishn, Somvaar se Shanivaar, shaam 7.30 baje, sirf #StarBharat par. Krishn aur Radha ki leelaon se judde rehne ke liye hamein follow kariye Instagram, Facebook aur YouTube par!

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3662 - 7 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3662: Jetha: The Kind One
--------------------------------------------------------
Bagha is melancholy after Bawri's decision to cut all ties. Bagha is taken back to Gada Electronics by Sodhi. Everyone tries to cheer Bagha up, but he seems traumatized. Nattu Kaka assigns him some work to keep his mind off Bawri, but Bagha commits a massive mistake in his work. Bagha's kind-hearted boss, Jethalal, tells Nattu Kaka to take care of Bagha while taking care of the shop. Nattu Kaka takes Bagha to their house and consoles him by talking about their village, but Bagha gets sad. How will Nattu Kaka handle Bagha and his emotions?

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3662, 7 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.description:
#pavbhaji #mumbaistyle #bhaji 

INGREIDENTS TO MAKE THE RECIPE:

2 Onions (Slices)
3 Desi Tomatoes 
1 Capsicum
1 Whole Garlic 
2 Inch Ginger 
2 - 3 Tbsp Butter 
Oil As Needed 
1 tsp Cumin Seeds 
1/2 tsp Turmeric Powder 
1 tsp Kashmiri Red Chilli Powder 
1 Tbsp Salt 
1/2 Beatroot 
1 - 2 Carrot 
1 Cup Peas
3 Potatoes 
250 - 300 Gms Cauli Flower 
1.5 Cups Water 
4 Tbsp Butter 
1 tsp Bleck Pepper Powder 
2 Tbsp Kasuri Methi 
 Coriander Leaves 

FOR TADKA 

3 - 4 Garlic Cloves (chopped )
1 Onion (Finely Chopped )
2 Tbsp Pav Bhaji Masala 

FOR PAV 

2 Tbsp Butter 
1 tsp Poav Bhaji Masala 
1/2 tsp Kashmiri Red Chilli Powder 
Coriander Leaves.
